                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Thames Police Inspector</hi>). I saw the prisoner standing on Tower Hill looking at the monkey—he commenced to run, I ran after him—Major said he had a watch in his pocket—I said, "Have you?"—he said, "No, I have not"—I searched him and found this watch in his left trousers pocket.</p>
